hadiths[192]{hadithnumber,text}:
2047,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadison bahut zyada bayan karta hai, aur ye bhi kehtey ho ke muhajireen w Ansar Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki tarah kyon hadis nahi bayan kartey? asl wjah ye hai ke mere bhai muhajireen bazar ki khareed w farokht mein mashghool raha kartey they. aur main apna pet bharney ke baad phir barabar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir rehta, isliye jab ye bhai ghair hazir hotey to main us waqt bhi hazir rehta aur main (wo baatein aap se sun kar) yad kar leta jisey un hazraat ko (apne karobar ki mashghooliyat ki wjah se ya to sunney ka mauqa nahi milta tha yaa) wo bhool jaya kartey they. isi tarah mere bhai Ansar apne maalon (kheton aur baaghon) mein mashghool rahtey, lekin main Suffa mein muqeem miskinon mein se aik miskeen aadmi tha. jab ye hazraat Ansar bhooltey to main usey yad rakhta. aik martaba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik hadis bayan kartey huey farmaya tha ke jo koi apna kapda phailaey aur us waqt tak phailaey rakhey jab tak apni ye guftgu na poori kar loon, phir (jab meri guftgu poori ho jaey to) us kapdey ko samet ley to wo meri baton ko (apne dil w dimagh mein hamesha) yad rakhega, chunanche maine apna kambal apne samney phaila diya, phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna maqaalaa Mubarak khatm farmaya, to maine usey samet kar apne seeney se laga liya aur uske baad phir kabhi mein aapki koi hadis nahi bhoolaa."
2048,"jab ham Madina aaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere aur Sad-bin-Rabee Ansari ke darmyan bhai chaara kara diya. Sad-bin-Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main Ansar ke sabse zyada maaldaar logon mein se hun. isliye apna aadha maal mein aapko deta hun aur aap khud dekh lein ke meri 2 beeviyon mein se aapko kon zyada pasand hai. main aapke liye unhein apne se alag kar doonga (yani talaaq de doonga) jab unki iddat poori ho jaey to aap unse nikah kar lein. bayan kya ke is par Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, mujhey unki zarurat nahi. kya yahan koi bazar hai jahan karobar hota ho? Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne ''Qainuqaa baazaar'' ka naam liya. bayan kya ke jab subah hui to Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) paneer aur ghi laey. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir wo tijarat ke liye bazar aaney janey lagey. kuchh dinon ke baad aik din wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to zard rang ka nishan (kapdey ya jism par) tha. Rasulullah ne malum farmaya kya tum ne shadi kar li hai? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kis se ? boley ke aik Ansari khatun se. malum farmaya aur mehar kitna diya hai? arz kya ke aik guthli barabar sona diya hai ya (ye kaha ke) soney ki aik guthli di hai. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, achchha to walima kar chahe aik bakri hi ka ho."
2049,"jab Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) Madina aaey, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka bhai-chara Sad-bin-Rabee Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se kara diya. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) maaldaar aadmi they. unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha, main aur aap mere maal se aadha aadhaa ley lein aur main (apni aik biwi se) aap ki shadi kara dun. Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne iske jawab mein kaha Allah Taala aap ke ahal aur aap ke maal mein barkat ata farmaaey, mujhey to aap bazar ka rasta bata dijiye, phir wo bazar se us waqt tak wapas na huey jab tak nafa mein kafi paneer aur ghi na bacha liya. ab wo apne ghar walon ke paas aaey kuchh din guzrey hongey ya Allah ne jitna chaha. iske baad wo aaey ke un par zardi ka nishan tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ye zardi kaisi hai? arz kya, ya Rasulullah! maine aik Ansari aurat se shadi kar li hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke unhein mehar mein kya diya hai? arz kya ''soney ki aik guthli'' ya (ye kaha ke) ''eik guthli barabar sona '' Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha ab walima kar, agarche aik bakri hi ka ho."
2050,"Ukaaz, Mujanna aur zul-Majaaz ahade-jaahiliyat ke bazar they. jab Islam aaya to aisa hua ke musalman log ( khareed w farokht ke liye un bazaron mein jana) gunah samajhney lagey. isliye ye aayat nazil hui ''tumhaarey liye usmein koi harj nahi agar tum apne rab ke Fazal (yani rizq halal ( ki talash karo Haj ke mausam mein'' ye Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki qirat hai."
2051,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya halal bhi khula hua hai aur haram bhi zahir hai lekin un donon ke darmyan kuchh mushtabah cheezein hain. to jo shakhs un chizon ko chhodey jinke gunah honey ya na honey mein shuba hai wo un chizon ko to zaroori hi chhod dega jinka gunah hona zahir hai lekin jo shakhs shuba ki chizon ke karne ki jur'at karega to qareeb hai ke wo un gunahon mein mubtala ho jaey jo bilkul waazeh taur par gunah hain ( logo yad rakho ( gunah Allah Taala ki charaagaah hai jo ( janwar bhi) charaagaah ke ird-gird charey ga uska charaagaah ke andar chala jana ghair mumkin nahi.
2052,"aik siyah faam khatun aaiin aur dawa kya ke unhon-ne un donon ( Aqba aur unki biwi ( ko doodh pilaya hai. Aqba ne is baat ka zikr Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna chehra Mubarak pher liya aur muskuraa kar farmaya, ab jabke aik baat keh di gaee to tum donon aik sath kis tarah reh saktey ho. unke nikah mein Abu-Abaab tamimi ki beti thin."
2053,"Utba-bin- abii-waqaas ( kaafir ( ne apne bhai Sad-bin-abi-Waqas ( musalman ( ko) martey waqt) wasiiyat ki thi ke Zam-aa ki baandi ka ladka mera hai. isliye usey tum apne qabze mein ley lenaa. unhon-ne kaha ke fateh Makka ke saal Sad (Raziallahu anhu) bin abii-waqaas ne usey ley liya, aur kaha ke ye mere bhai ka ladka hai aur wo iske mutaalliq mujhey wasiiyat kar gaey hain, lekin Abd-bin-Zam'a ne uth kar kaha ke mere bap ki londi ka bachcha hai, mere bap ke bistar par paida hua hai. aakhir donon ye muqaddima Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley gaey. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! ye mere bhai ka ladka hai aur mujhey uski unhon-ne wasiiyat ki thi aur Abd-bin-Zam'a ne arz kya, ye mera bhai hai aur mere bap ki londi ka ladka hai. unhiin ke bistar par uski paidaaish hui hai. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Abd-binZam'a ! ladka to tumharey hi sath rahega. iske baad farmaya, bachcha usi ka hota hai jo jaaiz shauhar ya Malik ho jiske bistar par wo paida hua ho. aur haram kaar ke hisse mein pattharon ki saza hai. phir Sauda-binte-Zama (Raziallahu anhu) se jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki biwi thin, farmaya ke us ladkey se parda kya kar, kyonke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Utba ki Shabaahat us ladkey mein mehsus kar li thi. iske baad us ladkey ne Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ko kabhi na dekha yahan tak ke wo Allah Taala se ja mila."
2054,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se teer ke shikar ke mutaalliq puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar iske dhaar ki taraf se lagey to kha . agar chaudai se lagey to mat kha . kyonke wo murdar hai, maine arz kya ya Rasulullah! main apna kutta ( shikar ke liye) chhorta hun aur bismillaah padh leta hon, phir iske sath mujhey aik aisa kutta aur milta hai jis par maine bismillaah nahi padhi hai. main ye faisla nahi kar paata ke donon mein kon se kuttey ne shikar pakda . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aisey shikar ka gosht na khaa. kyonke tu ney bismillaah to apne kuttey ke liye padhi hai. doosrey ke liye to nahi padhi."
2055,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik giri hui khajoor par guzrey, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar iske sadqa honey ka shuba na hota to main usey kha leta aur Hammam-bin-Munabba ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, main apne bistar par padi hui aik khajoor paata hun."
2056,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aik aisey shakhs ka zikr aaya jisey Namaz mein kuchh shuba hua nikalney ka ho jata hai. aaya usey Namaz tod deni chahiye ? farmaya ke nahi. jab tak wo awaz na sun ley ya badboo na mehsus kar ley (us waqt tak Namaz na todey ( ibne-abi Hafsa ne Zohri se bayan kya ( aisey shakhs par) wuzu wajib nahi jab tak hadas ki badboo na mehsus karey ya awaz na sun ley.
2057,kuchh logon ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! bahut se log hamarey yahan gosht latey hain. hamein ye malum nahi ke Allah ka naam unhon-ne zabah ke waqt liya tha ya nahi ? is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum bismillaah padh ke usey kha liya karo.
2058,ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Juma ki Namaz padh rahe they. (yani khutba sun rahe they) ke mulk Sham (Syria) se kuchh oont khaney ka saamaane-tijaarat lekar aaey. (sab namaazii) log unki taraf mutwajjeh ho gaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baara aadmiyon ke siwa aur koi baqi na raha. is par ye aayat nazil hui ( وإذا رأوا تجارة أو لهوا انفضوا إليها‏ ( '' jab wo maale-tijaarat ya koi tamasha dekhtey hain to uski taraf daud padtey hain.''
2059,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya logon par aik aisa zamana aayega ke insan koi parwah nahi karega ke jo usney hasil kya hai wo halal se hai ya haram se hai.
2060,"main soney-chaandii ki tijarat kya karta tha. isliye maine Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se iske mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur mujh se Fazal-bin-Ya'qoob ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham se hujjaaj-bin-Muhammad ne bayan kya ke ibne-Juraij ne bayan kya ke mujhey Amr-bin-Dinar aur aamir-bin-Mus'ab ne khabar di, un donon hazraat ne Abul-Minhaal se suna. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Bara-bin-Aazib aur Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se soney chandi ki tijarat ke mutaalliq poochha, to un donon buzurgon ne farmaya ke ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daur mein taajir they, isliye ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se soney chandi ke mutaalliq puchha tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab ye diya tha ke (lein-dein) hathon hath ho to koi harj nahi lekin udhaar ki sura mein jaaiz nahi hai."
2061,"main soney-chaandii ki tijarat kya karta tha. isliye maine Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se iske mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur mujh se Fazal-bin-Ya'qoob ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham se hujjaaj-bin-Muhammad ne bayan kya ke ibne-Juraij ne bayan kya ke mujhey Amr-bin-Dinar aur aamir-bin-Mus'ab ne khabar di, un donon hazraat ne Abul-Minhaal se suna. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Bara-bin-Aazib aur Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se soney chandi ki tijarat ke mutaalliq poochha, to un donon buzurgon ne farmaya ke ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daur mein taajir they, isliye ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se soney chandi ke mutaalliq puchha tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab ye diya tha ke (lein-dein) hathon hath ho to koi harj nahi lekin udhaar ki sura mein jaaiz nahi hai."
2062,"abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se milney ki ijazat chahi lekin ijazat nahi milii. ghaaliban aap us waqt kaam mein mashghool they. isliye abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) wapas lot gaey. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) farigh huey to farmaya kya maine Abdullah-bin-Qais (abu-Moosa (rz)) ki awaz nahi suni thi. unhein andar aaney ki ijazat de do. kaha gaya wo lot kar chaley gaey. to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bula liya. abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke hamein usi ka hukm (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se) tha (ke teen martaba ijazat chaahney par agar andar janey ki ijazat na miley to wapas lot jana chaahiye) is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, us hadis par koi gawah laao. abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) Ansar ki majlis mein gaey aur unse us hadis ke mutaalliq puchha (ke kya kisi ne usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai) un logon ne kaha ke uski gawahi to tumharey sath wo dega jo ham sab mein bahut hi kam Umr hai. wo Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ko apne sath ley gaey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye sun kar farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka aik hukm mujh se chipa reh gaya. afsos ke mujhey bazaron ki khareed w farokht ne mashghool rakha. aap ki murad tijarat se thi."
2063,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Bani-Israeel ke aik shakhs ka zikr kya. jisne samandar ka safar kya tha aur apni zarurat poori ki thi. phir poori hadis bayan ki.
2064,( tijarati ( oonton (ka qaafila ( aaya. ham us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Juma (ke khutba ( mein Sharik they. baara sahaba ke siwa baqi tamam hazraat udhar chaley gaey is par ye aayat utri ( وإذا رأوا تجارة أو لهوا انفضوا إليها وتركوك قائما ( '' jab sodagari ya tamasha dekhtey hain to uski taraf daud padtey hain aur aapko khada chhod detey hain.''
2065,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jab aurat apne ghar ka khana ( ghalla wghaira) basharte ke ghar bigadney ki niyat na ho kharch karey to usey kharch karne ka sawab milta hai aur uske shauhar ko kamaaney ka aur khazaanchii ko bhi aisa hi sawab milta hai aik ka sawab doosrey ke sawab ko kam nahi karta."
2066,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, agar aurat apne shauhar ki kamaaii uski ijazat ke baghair bhi) Allah ke rastey mein) kharch karti hai to usey aadha sawab milta hai."
2067,maine suna Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke jo shakhs apni rozii mein kushadgi chahta ho ya umr ki daraazii chahta ho to usey chahiye ke sila rehmii kare.
2068,Ibrahim Nakhai ki majlis mein ham ne udhaar lein-dein main ( saman ( girwii rakhney ka zikr kya to unhon-ne kaha ke mujh se Aswad ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik Yahudi se kuchh ghalla aik muddat muqarrar karke udhaar khareedaa aur apni lohey ki aik zirah uske paas girwii rakhii.
2069,"wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein jau ki roti aur badbudar charbi (saalan ke taur par) ley gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt apni zirah Madina mein aik Yahudi ke yahan girwii rakhi thi aur usse apne ghar walon ke liye qarz liya tha. maine khud aapko ye farmatey suna ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke gharaaney mein koi Sham aisi nahi aai jis mein unke paas aik saa gehun ya aik saa koi ghalla maujood raha ho, halanke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ghar waaliyon ki tadaad nau (9) thi."
2070,"jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khaleefa huey to farmaya, meri qaum janti hai ke mera (tijaaratii) karobar mere ghar walon ki guzraan ke liye kafi raha hai, lekin ab main musalmanon ke kaam mein mashghool ho gaya hon, isliye aale-abu-Bakar ab baitul-maal mein se khaaegii, aur Abu-Bakar musalmanon ka maal tijarat badhata rahega."
2071,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) apne kaam apne hi hathon se kya kartey they aur) zyada mehnat w mashaqqat ki wjah se) unke jism se ( pasiney ki) bo aa jati thi. isliye unse kaha gaya ke agar tum ghusl kar liya karo to behtar hoga. uski riwayat Hammam ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne apne bap se aur unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se ki hai.
2072,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kisi insan ne us shakhs se behtar rozii nahi khaai, jo khud apne hathon se kamaa kar khata hai Allah ke Nabi Dawud (Alaihissalam) bhi apne hath se kaam karke rozii khaya kartey they."
2073,Dawud (Alaihissalam) sirf apne hath ki kamaaii se khaya kartey they.
2074,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya wo shakhs jo lakdi ka ghataa apni peeth par laad kar laaey, us se behtar hai jo kisi ke samney hath phailaey chahe wo usey kuchh dedey ya na de."
2075,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar koi apni rassiyon ko sanbhaal ley aur unmein lakdi baandh kar laey to wo us se behtar hai jo logon se mangta phirtaa hai.
2076,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Allah Taala aisey shakhs par raham karey jo bechtey waqt aur khareedtey waqt aur taqaza kartey waqt faiyaazi aur narmii se kaam leta hai.
2077,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, tum se pahley pichhli ummaton ke kisi shakhs ki Rooh ke paas ( maut ke waqt) Farishtey aaey aur puchha ke tu ney kuchh achchhey kaam bhi kiye hain? Rooh ne jawab diya ke main apne naukaron se kaha karta tha ke wo maaldaar logon ko (jo unke maqrooz hon ( mohlat de diya karein aur un par sakhti na karein aur mohtajon ko maaf kar diya karein. rawi ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, phir farishton ne bhi us se darguzar kya aur sakhti nahi ki aur abu-Malik ne Rabaii se (apni riwayat mein ye alfaz ( bayan kiye hain'' khaatey kamatey ke sath (apnaa haq letey waqt) narm mamla karta tha aur tang haal maqrooz ko mohlat deta tha. uski mutabiat (pairavi) Shoba ne ki hai. unse Abdul-Malik ne aur unse Rabaii ne bayan kya, abu-Awana ne kaha ke unse Abdul-Malik ne Rabaii se bayan kya ke (is Rooh ne ye alfaz kahey they) main khaatey-kamaatey ko mohlat de deta tha aur tang haal waley maqrooz se darguzar karta tha aur Naeem-bin-abii-Hind ne bayan kya, unse Rabaii ne (ke Rooh ne ye alfaz kahey they) main khaatey-kamaatey logon ke (jin par mera koi haq wajib hotaa) uzr qabool kar liya karta tha aur tang haal waley se darguzar kar deta tha."
2078,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aik taajir logon ko qarz diya karta tha jab kisi tang dast ko dekhta to apne naukaron se keh deta ke us se darguzar kar jao . shayad ke Allah Taala bhi ham se (aakhirat mein) darguzar farmaaey. chunanche Allah Taala ne (iske marney ke baad) usko bakhsh diya."
2079,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kharidney aur bechney walon ko us waqt tak ikhtiyar (sauda khatm kar dene ka ( hai jab tak donon juda na hon ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( ما لم يتفرقا (ke bajaey) ( yahan tak يتفرقا ( farmaya, (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mazeed irshad farmaya) to agar donon ne sachchai se kaam liya aur har baat saaf-saaf khol di to unki khareed w farokht mein barkat hoti hai lekin agar koi baat chipa rakhi ya jhoot kahi to unki barkat khatm kar di jati hai."
2080,hamein (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se) mukhtalif qism ki khajoorein aik sath mila karti thin aur ham 2 saa khajoor aik saa ke badley mein bech diya kartey they. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke 2 saa aik saa ke badle mein na bechii jaey aur na 2 dirham aik dirham ke badley bechey jaaein.
2081,"Ansar mein se aik sahabi jinki kunniyat abu-Shuaib (Raziallahu anhu) thi, tashrif laey aur apne ghulam se jo qassaab tha. farmaya ke mere liye itna khana taiyaar kar jo panch aadmi ke liye kafi ho. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aur aap ke sath aur char aadmiyon ki dawat ka irada kya, kyonke maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra Mubarak par bhook ka asar numaayaan dekha hai. chunanche unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bulaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik aur sahib bhi aa gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hamarey sath aik aur sahib zyada aagey hain. magar aap chaahein to unhein bhi ijazat de saktey hain, aur agar chaahein to wapas kar saktey hain. unhon-ne kaha ke nahi, balke main unhein bhi ijazat deta hun."
2082,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, khareed-farokht karne walon ko ikhtiyar hai jab tak wo aik doosrey se juda na hon (ke Sauda khatm kar dein ya rakhein) ya aap ne ( ما لم يتفرقا (ke bajaey) ( yahan tak يتفرقا ( farmaya, isliye agar donon ne sachchai ikhtiyar ki aur har baat khol khol kar bayan ki to unki khareed-farokht mein barkat hogi aur agar unhon-ne kuchh chhipaaey rakha ya jhoot bola to unke khareed w farokht ki barkat khatm kar di jaeygi."
2083,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aik zamana aisa aayega ke insan uski parwah nahi karega ke maal usne kahan se liya, halal tariqa se ya haram tariqa se."
2084,jab ( sura ( Baqra ki aakhiri aayatein ( الذين يأكلون الربا * * * aakhiri aayat tak) nazil huin to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko masjid mein padh kar sunaya. iske baad un par sharab ki tijarat ko haram kar diya.
2085,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, raat ( khuwab mein) maine 2 aadmi dekhey , wo donon mere paas aaey aur mujhey baitul-maqdis mein le gaey, phir ham sab wahan se chaley yahan tak ke ham aik khoon ki nehar par aaey, wahan (nahar ke kinaarey) aik shakhs khada hua tha, aur nehar ke beech mein bhi aik shakhs khada tha. (nahar ke kinarey par) khadey hone-waale ke samney patthar padey huey they. beech nehar wala aadmi aata aur junhii wo chahta ke bahar nikal jaey fauran hi bahar wala shakhs uske munh par patthar kheench kar maarta jo usey wahin lota deta tha jahan wo pahley tha. isi tarah jab bhi wo nikalnaa chahta kinarey par khada hua shakhs iske munh par patthar kheench maarta aur wo jahan tha wahin phir lot jata. maine (apne sathiyon se jo Farishtey they) puchha ke ye kya hai, to unhon-ne iska jawab ye diya ke nehar main tum ne jis shakhs ko dekha wo sood khaney wala insan hai."
2086,"maine apne walid ko aik pachhna lagaaney wala ghulam khareedtey dekha. maine ye dekh kar unse iske mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne jawab diya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuttey ki qeemat leney aur khoon ki qeemat leney se mana farmaya hai, aap ne godney wali aur gudwaaney wali ko (godnaa lagwaaney se) sood leney waaley aur sood dene waaley ko) sood leney ya dene se) mana farmaya aur tasweer banaaney waley par laanat bhejii."
2087,maine khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna ke) saman bechtey waqt dukaandaar ke) qism khaney se saman to jaldi bik jata hai lekin wo qism barkat ko mitaa dene wali hoti hai.
2088,bazar mein aik shakhs ne aik saman dikhaa kar qism khaaii ke uski itni qeemat lag chuki hai. halanke uski itni qeemat nahi lagi thi is qism se iska maqsad aik musalman ko dhoka dena tha. is par ye aayat utri ( إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا ( ''jo log Allah ke ahad aur apni qasmon ko thodi qeemat ke badle mein bechtey hain.''
2089,ghaneemat ke maal mein se mere hissey mein aik oont aaya tha aur aik doosra oont mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ''khums'' mein se diya tha. phir jab mera irada Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ki rukhsati kara ke laney ka hua to maine bani qainuqaa' ke aik sunaar se tay kya ke wo mere sath chaley aur ham donon mil kar izkhir ghaas (jama karke) laaein kyonke mera irada tha ke usey sunaaron ke hath bech kar apni shadi ke waleeme mein uski qeemat ko lagaaun.
2090,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Allah Taala ne Makka ko hurmat wala Shahar qarar diya hai. ye na mujh se pahley kisi ke liye halal tha aur na mere baad kisi ke liye halal hoga. mere liye bhi aik din chand lamahaat ke liye halal hua tha. so ab uski na ghaas kaatii jaey, na iske darakht kaatey jaaein, na iske shikar bhagaaye jaaein, aur na usmein koi giri hui cheez uthai jaey. sirf gumshuda cheez ko asl Malik tak elaan ke zariey pahunchaney waley ko uski ijazat hai. Abbas bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke izkhir ke liye ijazat de dijiye , ke ye hamarey sunaaron aur hamarey gharon ki chhaton ke kaam mein aati hai. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne izkhir ki ijazat de di. Ikrima ne kaha, ye bhi malum hai ke haram ke shikar ko bhagaaney ka matlab kya hai? iska matlab ye hai ke) kisi darakht ke saaey taley agar wo betha hua ho to ( tum saaey se usey hata kar khud wahan baith jao. abdul-wahaab ne Khalid se (apni riwayat mein ye alfaz ( bayan kiye ke) izkhir ( hamarey sunaaron aur hamari qabron ke kaam mein aati hai."
2091,"jahiliyat ke zamane mein main lohaar ka kaam kya karta tha. Aas-bin-Waail ( kaafir ( par mera kuchh qarz tha mein aik din is par taqaza karne gaya. usne kaha ke jab tak to Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka inkar nahi karega mein tera qarz nahi doonga . maine jawab diya ke main aap ka inkar us waqt tak nahi karunga jab tak Allah Taala teri jaan na ley ley, phir to dobara uthaya jaey, usne kaha ke phir mujhey bhi mohlat de ke main mar jaun, phir dobara uthaya jaun aur mujhey maal aur aulad miley us waqt mein bhi tumhara qarz ada kar doonga . is par aayat nazil hui ( أفرأيت الذي كفر بآياتنا وقال لأوتين مالا وولدا * أطلع الغيب أم اتخذ عند الرحمن عهدا ( ''kya tum ne us shakhs ko dekha jisne hamari aayatein ko na maanaa aur kaha ( aakhirat mein) mujhey maal aur daulat di jaeygi, kya usey ghaib ki khabar hai? ya us ne Allah Taala ke yahan se koi iqrar ley liya hai.''"
2092,"aik darzii ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khaney par bulaya. Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, main bhi us dawat main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath gaya. us darzii ne roti aur shorba jis mein kadu aur bhunaa hua gosht tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney pesh kar diya. maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kadu ke qatley pyaley mein talash kar rahe they. isi din se main bhi barabar kadu ko pasand karta hun."
2093,"aik aurat ''burda'' lekar aai. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne poochha, tumhen malum bhi hai ke '' burda '' kisey kehtey hain. kaha gaya ji haan ! burda , haashiya daar chadar ko kehtey hain. to us aurat ne kaha, ya Rasulullah ! maine khas aapko pahnaaney ke liye ye chadar apne hath se bunii hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey ley liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski zarurat bhi thi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usi chadar ko bataur izaar ke pahney huey they, haaziriin mein se aik sahib boley, ya Rasulullah ! ye to mujhey de dijiye , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha ley lenaa. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) majlis mein thodi der tak baithey rahe phir wapas tashrif le gaey phir izaar ko teh karke un sahib ke paas bhijwa diya. logon ne kaha tum ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye izaar maang kar achchha nahi kya kyonke tumhen malum hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi saail ke sawal ko radd nahi kya kartey hain. is par un sahabi ne kaha ke Allah ki qism ! maine to sirf isliye ye chadar mangi hai ke jab main maroon to ye mera kafan baney. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke wo chadar hi unka kafan bani ."
2094,"kuchh log Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan mimbare-nabawii ke mutaalliq poochhney aaey. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne falan aurat ke yahan jinka naam bhi Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne liya tha, apna aadmi bheja ke wo apne badhaii ghulam se kahein ke mere liye kuchh lakdiyon ko jod kar member taiyaar kar de, taake logon ko waz (nasihat) karne ke liye mein is par baith jaya karun. chunanche us aurat ne apne ghulam se Ghaaba ke jhaau ki lakdi ka member banaaney ke liye kaha, phir (jab member taiyaar ho gaya to ( unhon-ne usey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhejaa. wo member Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se (masjid mein) rakha gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par baithey."
2095,"aik Ansari aurat ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya, ya Rasulullah! main aap ke liye koi aisi cheez kyon na banwaa dun jis par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) waz (nasihat) ke waqt betha karein. kyonke mere paas aik ghulam badhaii hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha tumhari marzii . rawi ne bayan kya ke phir jab member Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye us ne taiyaar kya. to Juma ke din jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us member par baithey to us khajoor ki lakdi se roney ki awaz aaney lagi jis par tek de kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pahley khutba diya kartey they. aisa malum hota tha ke wo phat jaeygi. ye dekh kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par se utrey aur usey pakad kar apne seeney se laga liya. us waqt bhi wo lakdi us chhotey bachchey ki tarah siskiyaan bhar rahi thi jisey chup karaaney ki koshish ki jati hai. iske baad wo chup ho gaee. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ke iske roney ki wjah ye thi ke ye lakdi khutba suna karti thi isliye rooii."
2096,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik Yahudi se kuchh ghalla udhaar khareedaa aur apni zirah uske paas girwii rakhwaaii.
2097,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik jang ( zaatur-Riqaa' ya Tabook ( mein tha. mera oont thak kar sust ho gaya. itney mein mere paas Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur farmaya Jaabir ! maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! hazir hun. farmaya kya baat huii? maine kaha ke mera oont thak kar sust ho gaya hai, chalta hi nahi isliye main peechhey reh gaya hun. phir aap apni sawari se utrey aur mere usi oont ko aik tedhey munh ki lakdi se kheenchney lagey (yani haankney lagey) aur farmaya ke ab Sawar ho jaa. chunanche main Sawar ho gaya. ab to ye haal hua ke mujhey usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke barabar pahunchne se roknaa pad jata tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, Jaabir tu ney shadi bhi kar li hai? maine kaha ji haan! malum farmaya kisi kunwari ladki se ki hai ya bewa se. maine arz kya ke maine to aik bewa se kar li hai. farmaya, kisi kunwari ladki se kyon na ki ke tum uske sath kheltey aur wo bhi tumharey sath kheltii. (Jaabir bhi kunwaarey they) maine arz kya ke meri kai bahnein hain. (aur meri maan ka intiqal ho chuka hai) isliye maine yahi pasand kya ke aisi aurat se shadi karun jo unhein jama rakhey. unke kangha karey aur unki nigrani kare. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha ab tum ghar pahunch kar khair w aafiyat ke sath khub mazey udaanaa. iske baad farmaya, kya tum apna oont bechogey? maine kaha ji haan! chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik auqiya chandi mein khareed liya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujh se pahley hi Madina pahunch gaey they. aur main doosrey din subah ko pahuncha . phir ham masjid aaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid ke darwaze par miley. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, kya abhi aaey ho? maine arz kya ke ji haan! farmaya, phir apna oont chhod de aur masjid mein jaake 2 rakaat Namaz padh. main andar gaya aur Namaz padhi. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke mere liye aik auqiya chandi tol de. unhon-ne aik auqiya chandi jhuktii hui tol di. main peeth mod kar chala to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Jaabir ko zara bulaao. maine sochaa ke shayad ab mera oont phir mujhey wapas karengey. halanke us se zyada na-gawar mere liye koi cheez nahi thi. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi farmaya ke ye apna oont ley ja aur uski qeemat bhi tumhari hai."
2098,"Ukaaz, Mujanna aur zul-Majaaz ye sab zamana jahiliyat ke bazar they. jab Islam aaya to logon ne unmein tijarat ko gunah samjha . is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki (ليس عليكم جناح‏ * * في مواسم الحج) ‏‏‏‏ Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne isi tarah qirat ki hai."
2099,yahan (Makka mein) aik shakhs nawaas naam ka tha. uske paas aik bimar oont tha. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) gaey aur uske Sharik se wahi oont khareed laey. wo shakhs aaya to iske saajhii ne kaha ke ham ne to wo oont bech diya. us ne puchha ke kisey bechaa? Sharik ne kaha ke aik Shekh ke hathon jo is tarah ke they. usne kaha afsos! wo to Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) they. chunanche wo aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya ke mere sathi ne aapko mareez oont bech diya hai aur aap se usne uske marz ki wazaahat bhi nahi ki. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke phir usey wapas ley jao. bayan kya ke jab wo usko ley janey laga to Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke achchha rehney do ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke faisle par razi hain (aap ne farmaya tha ke) beemaariyaan chhoot wali nahi hotiin) Ali-bin-Abdullaah madeenii ne kaha ke Sufiyan ne is riwayat ko Amr se suna.
2100,ham jange-Hunain ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nikley. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey aik zirah tohfa di aur maine usey bech diya. phir maine uski qeemat se qabila bani Salma mein aik baagh khareed liya. ye pehli jaaidaad thi jisey maine Islam laney ke baad hasil kya.
2101,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nek sathi aur burey sathi ki misal kastoori bechney waley attaar aur lohaar ki si hai. mashk bechney waley ke paas se tum 2 achchhaaiyon mein se aik na aik zaroor pa lo gey. ya to mashk hi khareed logey warna kam se kam uski khushbu to zaroor hi pa sakogey. lekin lohaar ki bhattii ya tumharey badan aur kapdey ko jhulsaa degi warna badboo to us se tum zaroor pa logey.
2102,abu-Taiba (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke pachhna lagaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik saa khajoor (bataur ujrat) unhein dene ke liye hukm farmaya aur unke Malik ko farmaya ke unke khiraaj mein kami kar dein.
2103,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pachhna lagwaayaa aur jisne pachhna lagaya usey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski ujrat bhi di, agar uski ujrat haram hoti to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usko hargiz na detey."
2104,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan aik reshamii jubba bhejaa. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) usey (eik din) pahney huey hain. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya maine usey tumharey paas isliye nahi bheja tha ke tum usey pahan lo, usey to wahi log pahntey hain jinka aakhirat mein koi hissey nahi. maine to isliye bheja tha ke tum us se (beech kar) fayda uthaao."
2105,"unhon-ne aik gaddaa khareedaa jis par moortein thin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nazar joon hi is par padii, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) darwazey par hi khadey ho gaey aur andar dakhil nahi huey. ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke) maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra Mubarak par na-pasandidgi ke aasaar dekhey to arz kya, ya Rasulullah! main Allah ki bargah mein tauba karti hun aur uske Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maafi maangtii hun, farmaiye mujh se kya ghalati hui hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ye gaddaa kaisa hai? maine kaha ke maine ye aap hi ke liye khareedaa hai taake aap is par baithein aur us se tek lagaaein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, lekin is tarah ki moortein banaaney waley log qiyamat ke din azab kiye jaeinge aur unse kaha jaeyga ke tum logon ne jis cheez ko banaya usey zinda kar dikhaao. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye bhi farmaya ke jin gharon mein tasweerein hoti hain (rahmat ke) Farishtey unmein dakhil nahi hotey."
2106,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey banu-Najjaar! apne baagh ki qeemat muqarrar kar do. (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us jagah ko masjid ke liye khareednaa chahtey they) us baagh mein kuchh hissey to weeraana aur kuchh hissey mein khajoor ke darakht they."
2107,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, khareed-farokht karne walon ko jab tak wo juda na hon ikhtiyar hota hai, ya khud saude mein ikhtiyar ki shart ho. (to shart ke mutabiq ikhtiyar hota hai) Naafe ne kaha ke jab Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) koi aisi cheez khareedtey jo unhein pasand hoti to (bechney ke baad) apne muaamla-daar se juda ho jatey."
2108,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, bechney aur kharidney walon ko jab tak wo juda na hon (muaamle ko baqi rakhney ya tod dene ka ( ikhtiyar hota hai. Ahmed ne ye zyadti ki ke hamse Behaz ne bayan kya ke Hammam ne bayan kya ke maine iska zikr Abu-Tayyah ke samney kya to unhon-ne batlaya ke jab Abdullah-bin-Haaris ne ye hadis bayan ki thi, to main bhi us waqt abul-Khaleel ke sath maujood tha."
2109,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kharidney waley aur bechney waley ko (sauda tod dene ka (us waqt tak ikhtiyar hai jab tak wo juda na ho jaaein. ya donon mein se koi aik apne doosrey fareeq se ye na keh de ke pasand kar lo. kabhi ye bhi kaha ke ''yaa ikhtiyar ki shart ke sath Sauda ho.''"
2110,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kharidney aur bechney waley jab tak aik doosrey se alag-alag na ho jayen unhein ikhtiyar baqi rehta hai. ab agar donon ne sachchai ikhtiyar ki aur har baat saaf-saaf bayan aur waazeh kar di, to unki khareed-farokht mein barkat hoti hai. lekin agar unhon-ne koi baat chhipaaii ya jhoot bola to unki khareed w farokht mein se barkat mitaa di jati hai."
2111,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kharidney aur bechney waley donon ko us waqt tak ikhtiyar hota hai, jab tak wo aik doosrey se juda na hun. magar Sauda khiyaar mein."
2112,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jab 2 shakhson ne khareed-farokht ki to jab tak wo donon juda na ho jaaein, unhein (saude ko tod dene ka ( ikhtiyar baqi rehta hai. ye is sura mein ke donon aik hi jagah rahein, lekin agar aik ne doosrey ko pasand karne ke liye kaha aur us shart par Sauda hua, aur donon ne saude ka qatae faisla kar liya, to Sauda usi waqt tay ho jaeyga isi tarah agar donon fareeq saude ke baad aik doosrey se juda ho gaey, aur saude se kisi fareeq ne bhi inkar nahi kya, to bhi Sauda lazim ho jata hai."
2113,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kisi bhi kharidney aur bechney waley mein us waqt tak Sauda pukhta nahi hoti jab tak wo donon juda na ho jaaein. albatta wo Sauda jis mein mushtarka ikhtiyar ki shart laga di gaee ho us se alag hai."
2114,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, bechney aur kharidney waley ko jab tak wo juda na hon (sauda tod dene ka ( ikhtiyar hai. Hammam rawi ne kaha ke maine apni kitab mein lafz ( يختار ( teen martaba likha hua paya. isliye agar donon ne sachchai ikhtiyar ki aur baat saaf-saaf waazeh kar di to unhein unke saude mein barkat miltii hai aur agar unhon-ne jhooti baatein banaaein aur (kisi aib ko) chhipaayaa to thoda sa nafa shayad wo kamaa lein, lekin unke saude mein barkat nahi hogi. ( Hibban ne) kaha ke ham se Hammam ne bayan kya, unse Abu-Tayyah ne bayan kya, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Haaris se suna ke yahi hadis wo Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) se b-hawaala Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) riwayat kartey they."
2115,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein they. main umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke aik naey aur sarkash oont par Sawar tha. aksar wo mujhey maghloob karke sabse aagey nikal jata, lekin umr (Raziallahu anhu) usey daant kar peechhey wapas kar detey. wo phir aagey badh jata. aakhir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke ye oont mujhey bech daal. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ya Rasulullah! ye to aap hi ka hai. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi mujhey ye oont de-dey. chunanche umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wo oont bech dala. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Abdullaah-bin-Umar! ab ye oont tera ho gaya jis tarah to chahey usey istemal kar."
2116,"maine ameerul-momineen Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko apni wadi Quraa ki zameen, unki khaibar ki zameen ke badley mein bechii thi. phir jab hamne Sauda kar liya to main ultey paon unke ghar se us khayal se bahar nikal gaya ke kahin wo Sauda faskh na kar dein. kyonke shariiat ka qaayeda ye tha ke bechney aur kharidney waley ko (sauda todney ka ( ikhtiyar us waqt tak rehta hai jab tak wo aik doosrey se juda na ho jaaein. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jab hamari khareed w farokht poori ho gaee aur maine ghaur kya to malum hua ke maine Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko nuqsan pahunchaya hai kyonke (is tabaadla ke nateejey mein, maine unki pehli zameen se) unhein teen din ke safar ki doori par Samood ki zameen ki taraf dhakel diya tha aur unhon-ne mujhey (meri masafat kam karke) Madina se sirf teen din ke safar ki doori par la chhoda tha."
2117,aik shakhs ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke wo aksar khareed w farokht mein dhoka kha jatey hain. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke jab tum kisi cheez ki khareed w farokht karo to yun keh diya karo ke '' bhai dhoka aur faraib ka kaam nahi. ''
2118,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, qiyamat ke qareeb aik lashkar Kaba par chadhai karega . jab wo maqam beda mein pahunchega to unhein awwal se aakhir tak sab ko zameen mein dhansaa diya jaeyga Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya, ke maine kaha, ya Rasulullah! usey shuru se aakhir tak kyon kar dhansaayaa jaeyga jabke wahin unke bazar bhi hongey aur wo log bhi hongey jawan lashkariyon mein se nahi hongey? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan! shuru se aakhir tak un sab ko dhansaa diya jaeyga phir unki niiyaton ke mutabiq wo uthaey jaengey."
2119,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jamat ke sath kisi ki Namaz bazar mein ya apne ghar mein Namaz padhney se darjon mein kuchh uper bees darjey zyada fazeelat rakhti hai. kyonke jab aik shakhs achi tarah wuzu karta hai phir masjid mein sirf Namaz ke irade se aata hai. Namaz ke siwa aur koi cheez usey ley janey ka baais nahi bantii to jo bhi qadam wo uthata hai us se aik darja iska buland hota hai ya uski wjah se aik gunah iska maaf hota hai aur jab tak aik shakhs apne musalley par betha rehta hai jis par us ne Namaz padhi hai to Farishtey barabar uske liye rehmat ki duaein yun kartey rahtey hain ( اللهم sl عليه , Mina padhi. اللهم ارحمه ( ''aey Allah ! is par apni rahmatein nazil farma, aey Allah is par raham farmaa.'' ye us waqt tak hota rehta hai jab tak wo wuzu tod kar farishton ko takleef na pahunchaaey jitni der tak bhi aadmi Namaz ki wjah se ruka rehta hai wo sab Namaz hi mein shumaar hota hai."
2120,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik martaba bazar mein they. aik shakhs ne pukara aey abul-Qaasim! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski taraf dekha. (kyonke aap ki kunniyat abul-Qaasim hi thi) is par us shakhs ne kaha ke maine to usko bulaya tha. (yani aik doosrey shakhs ko jo abul-Qaasim hi kunniyat rakhta tha) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum log mere naam par naam rakha karo lekin meri kunniyat tum apne liye na rakho.
2121,"aik shakhs ne Baqee main ( kisi ko) pukara ''aey abul-Qaasim '' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski taraf dekha, to us shakhs ne kaha ke maine aapko nahi pukaaraa. us doosrey aadmi ko pukara tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mere naam par naam rakha karo lekin meri kunniyat na rakha karo."
2122,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) din ke aik hisse mein tashrif ley chaley. na Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se koi baat ki aur na maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se. isi tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bani qainuqaa' ke bazar mein aaey phir ( wapas huey aur) Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar ke aangan mein baith gaey aur farmaya, wo bachcha kahan hai, wo bachcha kahan hai? Fatima (Raziallahu anha) (kisi mashghooliyat ki wjah se fauran) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir na ho sakiin. maine khayal kya, mumkin hai Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ko kurtaa wghaira pehna rahi hon ya rehlaa rahi hun. thodi hi der baad Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) daudtey huey aaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko seeney se laga liya aur bosa liya, phir farmaya aey Allaah! isey mahboob rakh aur us shakhs ko bhi mahboob rakh jo us se mohabbat rakhey. Sufiyan ne kaha ke Ubaidullah ne mujhey khabar di, unhon-ne Naafe'-bin-Jubair ko dekha ke unhon-ne witr ki Namaz sirf aik hi rakaat padhi thi."
2123,"sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein ghalla qaaflon se khareedtey they, to aap unke paas koi aadmi bhej kar wahin par jahan unhon-ne ghalla khareedaa hota. us ghalley ko bechney se mana farma detey aur usey wahan se la kar bechney ka hukm hota jahan aam taur par ghalla biktaa tha."
2124,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne poori tarah apne qabze mein karne se pahley usey bechney se mana farmaya,"
2125,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jo sifaat Taurait mein aai hain unke mutaalliq mujhey kuchh bataiye . unhon-ne kaha ke haan! qism Allah ki ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Taurait mein bilkul kuchh wahi sifaat aai hain jo Quran sharif mein mazkoor hain. jaisey ke ''aey nabii! ham ne tumhen gawaah, khushkhabri dene waalaa, daraane waalaa, aur un-padh qaum ki hifazat karne wala bana kar bheja hai. tum mere bandey aur mere rasool ho. maine tumhara naam mutawakkil rakha hai. tum na badkhoo ho, na sakht dil aur na bazaron mein shor-ghul machaaney waale, (aur Taurait mein ye bhi likha hua hai ke) wo (meraa banda aur rasool) burai ka badla burai se nahi lega. balke maaf aur darguzar karega. Allah Taala us waqt tak uski Rooh qabz nahi karega jab tak tedhii shariiat ko us se seedhi na kara ley, yani log ( لا إله إلا الله ( na kehney lagein aur uske zariey wo andhii aankhon ko dekhnewaalaa, behrey kanon ko sunnewaalaa aur parda padey huey dilon ko pardey khol dega. is hadis ki mutabiat (pairavi) abdul-Azeez-bin-abii-Salma ne Hilal se ki hai. aur Saeed ne bayan kya ke unse Hilal ne, unse Ata ne ke (ghalaf) har us cheez ko kehtey hain jo pardey mein ho. ( سيف أغلف ‏‏‏‏ وقوس غلفاء ) usii se hai aur) رجل أغلف (us shakhs ko kehtey hain jiska khatna na hua ho."
2126,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jab koi shakhs kisi qism ka ghalla khareedey to jab tak is par poori tarah qabza na kar ley, usey na bechey."
2127,"jab Abdullaah-bin-Amr-bin haram (Raziallahu anhu) (mere baap) Shahid ho gaey to unke zimmey (logon ka ( kuchh qarz baqi tha. isliye maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zariey koshish ki ke qarz denewaaley kuchh apne qarzon ko maaf kar dein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi chaha, lekin wo nahi maaney. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ke jao apni tamam khajoor ki qismon ko alag alag kar lo. ajwa (eik khas qism ki khajoor) ko alag rakh aur Azqe-zaid ( khajoor ki aik qism) ko alag kar. phir mujhey bulwa lenaa. maine aisa hi kya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kelha bhejaa. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur khajooron ke dher par ya beech mein baith gaey aur farmaya ke ab un qarz-khaahon ko naap kar do. maine naapnaa shuru kya. jitna qarz logon ka tha. maine sab ko ada kar diya, phir bhi tamam khajoor joon ki toon thi. usmein se aik daana barabar ki kami nahi hui thi. faraas ne bayan kya ke unse Shabi ne, aur unse Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke ''baraabar unke liye taultey rahe, yahan tak ke unka pura qarz ada ho gayaa.'' aur Hisham ne kaha, unse Wahab ne, aur unse Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, khajoor tod aur apna qarz pura ada kar de."
2128,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, apne ghalley ko naap liya karo. usmein tumhen barkat hogi."
2129,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Ibrahim ne Makka ko haram qarar diya aur uske liye dua farmai. main bhi Madina ko isi tarah haram qarar deta hun jis tarah Ibrahim ne Makka ko haram qarar diya tha aur uske liye, iske mudd aur saa ( ghalla naapney ke 2 paimaaney ( ki barkat ke liye is tarah dua karta hun jis tarah Ibrahim ne Makka ke liye dua ki thi."
2130,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey Allaah! unhein unke paimaanon mein barkat de, aey Allaah! unhein unke saa aur mudd mein barkat de. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad Madina waaley they."
2131,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein un logon ko dekha jo anaaj ke dher ( baghair toley huey mahz andaza karke ( khareed letey unko mar padtii thi. isliye ke jab tak apne ghar na ley jayen na bachein .
2132,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghalle par poori tarah qabza se pahley usey bechney se mana farmaya, Taaus ne kaha ke maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke aisa kyon hai? to unhon-ne farmaya ke ye to rupye ka rupyon ke badley bechna hua jabke abhi ghalla to meeaad hi par diya jaeyga abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke) marjioon ( se murad ( muakhkhiroon ( yani derii karna hai."
2133,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs bhi koi ghalla khareedey to is par qabza karne se pahley usey na bechey.
2134,"aap logon mein se koi Sauda sirf (yani diinaar, dirham, ashrafii wghaira badalney ka kaam) karta hai. Talha ne kaha ke main karta hun, lekin us waqt kar sakunga jabke hamara khazaanchii Ghaaba se aa jaeyga Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke Zohri se ham ne isi tarah hadis yad ki thi. usmein koi zyadti nahi thi. phir unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey Maalik-bin-Aos ne khabar di ke unhon-ne umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se suna. wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se naql kartey they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, sona soney ke badley main ( khareednaa ( sood mein dakhil hai magar ye ke naqd ho. geihun, gehun ke badley main ( khareednaa bechna ( sood mein dakhil hai magar ye ke naqd ho, khajoor, khajoor ke badley mein sood hai magar ye ke naqd ho aur jau, jau ke badley mein sood hai magar ye ke naqd ho."
2135,"maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye farmatey suna tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jis cheez se mana farmaya tha, wo us ghalle ka Sauda tha jis par abhi qabza na kya gaya ho, Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, main to tamam chizon ko usi ke hukm mein samajhta hun."
2136,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jo shakhs bhi jab ghalla khareedey to jab tak usey poori tarah qabze mein na ley ley, na bechey. Ismail ne ye zyadti ki hai ke jo shakhs koi ghalla khareedey to is par qabza karne se pahley na bechey."
2137,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak mein dekha ke logon ko is par tanbeeh ki jati jab wo ghalle ka dher khareed karke apne thikaaney par laney se pahley hi usko bech daaltey.
2138,"aisey din (makki zindagi mein) bahut hi kam aaey, jin main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah w Sham mein kisi na kisi waqt Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar tashrif na laey hun. phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Madina ki taraf hijrat ki ijazat di gaee, to hamari ghabraahat ka sabab ye hua ke aap ( mamool (routine) ke khilaf achcha ( Zohar ke waqt hamarey ghar tashrif laey. jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aamad ki itlaa di gaee to unhon-ne bhi yahi kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt hamarey yahan koi nai baat pesh aaney hi ki wjah se tashrif laey hain. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us waqt jo log tumharey paas hon unhein hata do. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! yahan to sirf meri yahi 2 betiyaan hain yani Aaisha aur Asma (rz). ab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen malum bhi hai mujhey to yahan se nikalney ki ijazat mil gaee hai. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya mere paas 2 oontniyan hain jinhein maine nikalney hi ke liye taiyaar kar rakha tha. aap unmein se aik ley lijiye . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha, qeemat ke badley mein, maine aik ontni ley li."
2139,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, koi shakhs apne bhai ki khareed-farokht mein dakhal andazi na kare."
2140,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana farmaya ke koi shehri kisi dehati ka maal w asbaab bechey aur ye ke koi (saamaan kharidney ki niyat ke baghair doosrey asl khareedaaron se) badh kar bolii na de. isi tarah koi shakhs apne bhai ke saudey mein mudaakhlat na kare. koi shakhs ( kisi aurat ko) doosrey ke paighaame-nikaah hotey huey apna paigham na bhejey aur koi aurat apni kisi deeni behan ko us niyat se talaaq na dilwaaey ke iske hisse ko khud hasil kar ley.
2141,"aik shakhs ne apna aik ghulam apne marney ke baad ki shart ke sath aazad kya. lekin ittifaq se wo shakhs muflis ho gaya, to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske ghulam ko lekar farmaya ke isey mujh se kon khareedega. is par Naeem-bin-Abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey itni itnii qeemat par khareed liya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghulam unke hawale kar diya."
2142,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dhokadhadi se mana farmaya tha.
2143,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamal ke hamal ke Sauda se mana farmaya, us saude ka tariqa jahiliyat mein raaij tha. aik shakhs aik oont ya ontni khareedtaa aur qeemat dene ki meeaad ye muqarrar karta ke aik ontni janey phir iske pet ki ontni badi ho kar janey."
2144,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne munaabiza ke saudey se mana farmaya tha. iska tariqa ye tha ke aik aadmi bechney ke liye apna kapda doosrey shakhs ki taraf (jo khareedaar hota ( phainktaa aur us se pahley ke wo usey ultey paltey ya uski taraf dekhey ( sirf phenk dene ki wjah se wo Sauda lazim samjha jata tha) isi tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Sauda mulaamisa se bhi mana farmaya, iska ye tariqa tha ke) kharidney wala) kapdey ko baghair dekhey sirf usey chhu deta (aur usi se Sauda lazim ho jati thi isey bhi dhoka ka Sauda qarar diya gaya."
2145,"2 tarah ke libaas pahnney mana hain. ke koi aadmi aik hi kapdey mein gote mar kar baithey, phir usey moondey par utha kar daal ley (aur sharmgah khuli rahe) aur 2 tarah ke saudey se mana kya aik Sauda mulaamisa se aur dusri Sauda munaabiza se."
2146,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Sauda mulaamisa aur Sauda munaabiza se mana farmaya,"
2147,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 tarah ke libaas se mana farmaya, aur 2 tarah ke saudey se, Sauda mulaamisa aur Sauda munaabiza se mana farmaya,"
2148,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (bechney ke liye) ontni aur bakri ke thanon mein doodh ko rok kar na rakho. agar kisi ne ( dhoke mein aa kar) koi aisa janwar khareed liya to usey doodh dohney ke baad donon ikhtiyaaraat hain chahey to janwar ko rakh ley, aur chahey to wapas kar de. aur aik saa khajoor iske sath doodh ke badal de-dey. abu-Saaleh, Mujaahid, Waleed bin Ribah aur Musa bin Yasar se b-waaste Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat aik saa khajoor hi ki hai. kuchh rawiyon ne Ibne-Sirin se aik saa khajoor ki riwayat ki hai aur ye ke khareedaar ko (soorate-mazkoora mein) teen din ka ikhtiyar hoga. agarche kuchh doosrey rawiyon ne Ibne-Sirin hi se aik saa khajoor ki bhi riwayat ki hai, lekin teen din ke ikhtiyar ka zikr nahi kya aur (taawaan mein) khajoor dene ki riwayat hi zyada hain."
2149,jo shakhs bakri khareedey aur usey wapas karna chahey to (asl Malik ko) iske sath aik saa bhi de. aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qaafile walon se (jo maal bechney laaein) aagey badh kar kharidney se mana farmaya hai.
2150,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (tijaaratii) qaaflon ki peshwai (unka saman Shahar pahunchey se pahley hi khareed leney ki gharaz se) na karo. aik shakhs kisi doosrey ke saudey par Sauda na karey aur koi dhoka aur faraib na karey aur koi shahrii, badwi ka maal na bechey aur bakri ke than mein doodh na rokey. lekin agar koi us (aakhirii) sura mein janwar khareed ley to usey dohney ke baad donon tarah ke ikhtiyaaraat hain. agar wo us saude par razi hai to janwar ko rok sakta hai aur agar wo razi nahi to aik saa khajoor iske sath de kar usey wapas kar de."
2151,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jis shakhs ne bakri kharidi aur usey dohaa. to agar wo us maamle par razi hai to usey apne liye rok ley aur agar razi nahi hai to ( wapas kar de aur) iske doodh ke badley mein aik saa khajoor de-dey.
2152,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab koi baandi zina karey aur uske zina ka saboot ( sharaee ( mil jaey to usey kode lagwaaey, phir uski laanat malaamat na kare. iske baad agar phir wo zina karey to phir kode lagwaaey magar phir laanat malaamat na kare. phir agar teesri martaba bhi zina karey to usey bech de chahey baal ki aik rassii ke badle hi mein kyon na ho."
2153,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya ke agar koi ghair shadi shuda baandi zina karey (to iska kya hukm hai) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey kode lagaao . agar phir zina karey to phir kode lagaao . phir bhi agar zina karey to usey bech do, agarche aik rassii hi ke badley mein wo bikey. ibne-Shahab ne kaha ke mujhey ye malum nahi ke (bechney ke liye) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teesri martaba farmaya tha ya chothi martaba."
2154,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya ke agar koi ghair shadi shuda baandi zina karey (to iska kya hukm hai) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey kode lagaao. agar phir zina karey to phir kode lagaao. phir bhi agar zina karey to usey bech do, agarche aik rassii hi ke badley mein wo farokht ho. ibne-Shahab ne kaha ke mujhey ye malum nahi ke (bechney ke liye) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teesri martaba farmaya tha ya chothi martaba ."
2155,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (Bareera (Raziallahu anhu) ke kharidney ka ( zikr kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum khareed kar aazad kar do. 'walaa' to usi ki hoti hai jo aazad kare. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par tashrif laey aur farmaya'' logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke) khareed w farokht mein) aisi shartein lagaatey hain jinki koi asl kitabullah mein nahi hai jo shakhs bhi koi aisi shart lagaaeyga jiski asl kitabullah mein na ho wo shart baatil hogi. chahe so shartein hi kyon na laga ley kyonke Allah hi ki shart haq aur mazbut hai (aur usi ka eitibaar hai).''
2156,"Aaisha (rz), Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ki (jo baandi thin )qeemat laga rahi thin (taake unhein khareed kar aazad kar dein) ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye (masjid mein) tashrif ley gaey. phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke (Bareera (Raziallahu anhu) ke maalikon ne to) apne liye 'walaa' ki shart ke baghair unhein bechney se inkar kar diya hai. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke 'walaa' to usi ki hoti hai jo aazad kare. maine Naafe se puchha ke Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke shauhar aazad they ya ghulaam, to unhon-ne farmaya ke mujhey malum nahi."
2157,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se is baat ki shahadat par ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke rasool hain. aur Namaz qaaim karne aur zakat dene aur (apne muqarrara ameer ki baat) sunney aur uski itaat karne par aur har musalman ke sath khair-khahi karne ki bait ki thi.
2158,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (tijaaratii) qaaflon se aagey ja kar na mila karo (unko mandi mein aaney 2) aur koi shahrii, kisi dehati ka saman na bechey, unhon-ne bayan kya ke is par maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us irshad ka ke ''koii shehri kisi dehati ka maal na bechey'' ka matlab kya hai? to unhon-ne farmaya ke matlab ye hai ke uska dalaal na baney."
2159,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana farmaya ke koi shehri , kisi dehati ka maal bechey . yahi Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi kaha hai."
2160,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, koi shakhs apne kisi bhai ke mol par mol na karey aur koi ( نجش ( ) dhoka , faraib ( na karey, aur na koi shehri , kisi dehati ke liye bechey ya mol ley."
2161,hamein us se rokaa gaya ke koi shehri kisi dehati ka maale-tijaarat bechey .
2162,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( tijarati qaaflon se) aagey badh kar milney se mana farmaya hai aur basti walon ko bahar walon ka maal bechney se bhi mana farmaya,"
2163,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us irshad ka matlab kya hai ke koi shehri kisi dehati ka maal na bechey? to unhon-ne kaha ke matlab ye hai ke uska dalaal na baney.
2164,jo koi doodh jama ki hui bakri khareedey (wo bakri pher de) aur uske sath aik saa dedey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qaafile walon se aagey badh kar milney se mana farmaayaa.
2165,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya koi shakhs kisi doosrey ke saudey par Sauda na karey aur jo maal bahar se aa raha ho us se aagey ja kar na miley jab tak wo bazar mein na aaey.
2166,"ham aagey qaaflon ke paas khud hi pahunch jaya kartey they aur (shahar mein pahunchne se pahley hi) unse ghalla khareed liya kartey, lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein is baat se mana farmaya ke ham us maal ko usi jagah bechein jab tak anaaj ke bazar mein na laaein . imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ka ye milnaa bazar ke buland kinarey par tha. (jidhar se sodagar aaya kartey they) aur ye baat Ubaidullah ki hadis se nikalti hai."
2167,"ham se Musaddad ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham se Yahya bin qattaan ne bayan kya, unse Ubaidullah ne, kaha ke mujh se Naafe ne bayan kya, aur unse Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke log bazar ki bulandi ki taraf jaakar ghallaa kharidney aur bechney lagtey. isliye rasooullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne issey manaa Farmaya ke ghalla wahan n bechein jab tak usko uthwaakar dusri jagah na le jaaein."
2168,"mere paas Barira (Raziallahu anhu) (jo us waqt tak baandi thiin) aaein aur kehney lagiin ke maine apne maalikon se nau (9) auqiya chandi par kitabat kar li hai. shart ye hui hai ke har saal aik auqiya chandi unhein diya karun. ab aap bhi meri kuchh madad keejiye. is par maine us se kaha ke agar tumharey Malik ye pasand karein ke eik-musht unka sab rupya mein unke liye ( abhi ( muhaiya kar dun aur tumhara tarka mere liye ho to main aisa bhi kar sakti hun. Barira (Raziallahu anhu) apne maalikon ke paas gain aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki tajwiz unke samney rakhii. lekin unhon-ne us se inkar kya, phir Barira (Raziallahu anhu) unke yahan wapas aaiin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan ( baithey huey they. unhon-ne kaha ke maine to aap ki sura unke samney rakhi thi magar wo nahi mantey balke kehtey hain ke tarka to hamara hi rahega. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye baat suni aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bhi aapko haqeeqate-haal se khabar ki. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Barira ko tum ley lo aur unhein tarke ki shart lagaaney do. tarka to usi ka hota hai jo aazad karaye. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne aisa hi kya. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uth kar logon ke majme' mein tashrif le gaey aur Allah ki hamd w sana ke baad farmaya, ammaa ba'd! kuchh logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke wo (khareed w farokht mein) aisi shartein lagaatey hain jinki kitabullah mein koi asl nahi hai. jo koi shart aisi lagai jaey jiski asl kitabullah mein na ho wo baatil hogi. chahe aisi so shartein koi kyon na lagaey. Allah Taala ka hukm sab par muqaddam hai aur Allah ki shart hi bahut mazbut hai aur 'walaa' to usi ki hoti hai jo aazad kare."
2169,"Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne chaha ke aik baandi ko khareed kar aazad kar dein, lekin unke maalikon ne kaha ke ham unhein us shart par aapko bech saktey hain ke unki 'walaa' hamarey sath rahe. iska zikr jab Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us shart ki wjah se tum hargiz na rukoo . 'walaa' to usi ki hoti hai jo aazad kare."
2170,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, gehun ko gehun ke badle mein bechna sood hai, lekin ye ke saudaa hathon hath ho. jau ko jau ke badle mein bechna sood hai, lekin ye ke hathon hath ho. aur khajoor ko khajoor ke badle mein bechna sood hai lekin ye ke saudaa hathon haath, naqd ho."
2171,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzaabna se mana farmaya, Muzaabna ye ke darakht par lagi hui khajoor khushk khajoor ke badla maap karke bechii jaey. isi tarah bail par lagey huey angoor ko munaqqaa ke badal bechna ."
2172,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzaabna se mana farmaya, unhon-ne bayan kya ke Muzaabna ye hai ke koi shakhs darakht par ki khajoor sokhii khajoor ke badal maap-taul kar bechey aur khareedaar kahey agar darakht ka phal us sookhey phal se zyada nikley to wo uska hai aur kam nikley to wo nuqsan bhar dega."
2173,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey araayaa ki ijazat de di thi jo andaazey hi se saude ki aik sura hai.
2174,"unhein 100 ashrafiyaan bdalnii thin. (unhon-ne bayan kya ke) phir mujhey Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne bulaya aur ham ne (apne maamle ki) baat cheet ki. aur unse mera mamla tay ho gaya. wo soney (ki ashrafiyon) ko apne hath mein lekar ulatney-palatney lagey aur kehney lagey ke zara mere khazaanchii ko Ghaaba se aa leney do. umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi hamari baatein sun rahe they, aap ne farmaya : Allah ki qasam! jab tak tum Talha se rupya ley na lo, unse juda na hona kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai ke sona soney ke badle mein agar naqd na ho to sood ho jata hai. geihun, gehun ke badley mein agar naqd na ho to sood ho jata hai. jau, jau ke badle mein agar naqd na ho to sood ho jata hai aur khajoor, khajoor ke badle mein agar naqd na ho to sood ho jati hai."
2175,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, sona soney ke badley mein us waqt tak na becho jab tak (donon taraf se) baraabar-baraabar (ki lein-dein) na ho. isi tarah chaandii, chandi ke badle mein us waqt tak na becho jab tak (donon taraf se) barabar barabar na ho. albatta sonaa, chandi ke badal aur chandi soney ke badal mein jis tarah chaho becho."
2176,"(jaisey Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ya umr (Raziallahu anhu) se guzrii) phir aik martaba Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki unse mulaqat hui to unhon-ne poochha, aey abu-Saeed! aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se ye kon si hadis bayan kartey hain? Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke hadis sauda-sarf (yani rupya ashrafiyaan badalney ya tudwaaney) se mutaalliq hai. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka farman suna tha ke sona soney ke badley mein barabar barabar hi bechaa ja sakta hai aur chaandii, chandi ke badle mein baraabar-baraabar hi bechii ja sakti hai."
2177,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, sona soney ke badley us waqt tak na becho jab tak donon taraf se baraabar-baraabar na ho, donon taraf se kisi kami ya zyadti ko munasib na rakho, aur chandi ko chandi ke badley mein us waqt tak na becho jab tak donon taraf se barabar barabar na ho. donon taraf se kisi kami ya zyadti ko munasib na rakho aur na udhaar ko naqd ke badley mein becho."
2178,"diinaar, Dinar ke badley main aur dirham, dirham ke badley mein (bechaa ja sakta hai) is par maine unse kaha ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) to uski ijazat nahi detey. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se iske mutaalliq puchha ke aap ne ye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha ya kitabullah mein aap ne usey paya hai? unhon-ne kaha ke unmein se kisi baat ka main dawedar nahi hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ki ahaadees) ko aap log mujh se zyada jantey hain. albatta mujhey Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (mazkoora Suraton mein) sood sirf udhaar ki sura mein hota hai."
2179,"diinaar, Dinar ke badley main aur dirham, dirham ke badley mein (bechaa ja sakta hai) is par maine unse kaha ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) to uski ijazat nahi detey. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se iske mutaalliq puchha ke aap ne ye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha ya kitabullah mein aap ne usey paya hai? unhon-ne kaha ke unmein se kisi baat ka main dawedar nahi hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ki ahaadees) ko aap log mujh se zyada jantey hain. albatta mujhey Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (mazkoora Suraton mein) sood sirf udhaar ki sura mein hota hai."
2180,maine Bara-bin-Aazib aur Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se sauda-sarf ke mutaalliq puchha to un donon hazraat ne aik doosrey ke mutaalliq farmaya ke ye mujh se behtar hain. aakhir donon hazraat ne batlaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne soney ko chandi ke badley mein udhaar ki sura mein bechney se mana farmaya hai.
2181,maine Bara-bin-Aazib aur Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se sauda-sarf ke mutaalliq puchha to un donon hazraat ne aik doosrey ke mutaalliq farmaya ke ye mujh se behtar hain. aakhir donon hazraat ne batlaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne soney ko chandi ke badley mein udhaar ki sura mein bechney se mana farmaya hai.
2182,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chandi , chandi ke badley main aur sona soney ke badley mein bechney se mana farmaya hai. magar ye ke barabar barabar ho. albatta sona chandi ke badley mein jis tarah chaahein khareedein . isi tarah chandi soney ke badley jis tarah chaahein khareedein ."
2183,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, phal ( darakht par ka (us waqt tak na becho jab tak iska pakka hona na khul jaey. aur darakht par lagi hui khajoor ko khushk khajoor ke badley mein na becho ."
2184,baad main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sauda-ariya ki tar ya khushk khajoor ke badle mein ijazat de di thi lekin iske siwa kisi sura ki ijazat nahi di thi.
2185,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzaabna se mana farmaya, Muzaabna darakht par lagi hui khajoor ko tootii hui khajoor ke badley naap kar aur darakht ke angoor ko khushk angoor ke badley mein naap kar bechney ko kehtey hain."
2186,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzaabna aur Muhaaqla se mana farmaya, Muzaabna darakht par lagi khajoor , todii hui khajoor ke badley mein kharidney ko kehtey hain."
2187,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muhaaqla aur Muzaabna se mana farmaayaa.
2188,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saahibe-ariya ko uski ijazat di ke apna ariya iske andaazey barabar mewey ke badal beech daley.
2189,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajoor ke pakney se pahley bechney se mana kya hai aur ye ke usmein se zarra barabar bhi dirham w denaar ke siwa kisi aur cheez (sookhey phal) ke badley na bechii jaey albatta ariya ki ijazat di.
2190,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne panch wasq ya us se kam mein Sauda ariya ki ijazat de di hai? to unhon-ne kaha ke haan!
2191,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne darakht par lagi hui khajoor ko todii hui khajoor ke badley bechney se mana farmaya, albatta ariya ki Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ijazat di ke andaza karke ye Sauda kiya ja sakta hai ke ariya waley iske badal taaza khajoor khaaein. Sufiyan ne dusri martaba ye riwayat bayan ki, lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ariya ki ijazat de di thi. ke andaza karke ye Sauda kiya ja sakta hai, khajoor hi ke badley mein. donon ka mafhoom aik hi hai. Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke maine Yahya se poochha, us waqt main abhi kam Umr tha ke Makka ke log kehtey hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ariya ki ijazat di hai to unhon-ne puchha ke ahale-Makka ko ye kis tarah malum hua? maine kaha ke wo log Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain. is par wo khamosh ho gaey. Sufiyan ne kaha ke meri murad isse ye thi ke Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) Madina waley hain. Sufiyan se puchha gaya ke kya unki hadis mein ye manaahii nahi hai ke phalon ko bechney se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya jab tak unki pukhtagi na khul jaey unhon-ne kaha ke nahi."
2192,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ariya ki ijazat di ke wo andaazey se bechii ja sakti hai. Musa-bin-Aqba ne kaha ke araayaa kuchh muaiyan darakht jinke mewe to utrey huey mewey ke badal khareedey.
2193,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein log phalon ki khareed w farokht (darakhton par pakney se pahley) kartey they. phir jab phal todney ka waqt aataa, aur Malik (qeemat ka ( taqaza karne aatey to khareedaar ye uzr karne lagtey ke pahley hi iska gabha kharaab aur kala ho gaya, usko bimari ho gaee, ye to thithar gaya phal bahut hi kam aaey. isi tarah mukhtalif aafaton ko bayan karke maalikon se jhagadtey (taake qeemat mein kami kara lein) jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas is tarah ke muqaddamaat kasrat se aaney lagey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab is tarah jhagdey khatm nahi ho saktey to tum log bhi mewe ke pakney se pahley unko na bechaa karo. maano muqaddamaat ki kasarat ki wjah se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye bataur mashwara farmaya tha. khaarija-bin-Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey khabar di ke Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) apne baagh ke phal us waqt tak nahi bechtey jab tak surayyaa (naamii sitaaraa) na nikal aata aur zardi aur surkhi zahir na ho jati. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke uski riwayat Ali-bin-Bahar ne bhi ki hai ke ham se hakkaam-bin-Salam ne bayan kya, unse anbasaa ne bayan kya, unse Zakariya ne, unse abu-Zinaad ne, unse Urwa ne aur unse Sahal-bin-Sad ne aur unse Zaid-bin-Saabit ne."
2194,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pukhta honey se pahley phalon ko bechney se mana kya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki manaahii bechney waley aur kharidney waley donon ko thi.
2195,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pakney se pahley darakht par khajoor ko bechney se mana farmaya hai, abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke (حتى تزهو) se) murad ye hai ke jab tak wo paak kar surkh na ho jaaein."
2196,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phalon ka ( تشقح‏ . Mina ( se pahley bechney se mana kya tha. puchha gaya ke) تشقح‏ . Mina ( kisey kehtey hain to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke zard ya surkh honey ko kehtey hain ke usey khaya ja sakey (phal ka pukhta hona murad hai).
2197,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pukhta honey se pahley phalon ko bechney se mana farmaya hai aur khajoor ke baagh ko) زهو ( se pahley bechney se mana farmaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya ke) زهو ( kisey kehtey hain to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab diya surkh ya zard honey ko kehtey hain."
2198,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phalon ko) زهو ( se pahley bechney se mana farmaya hai. unse puchha gaya ke) زهو ( kisey kehtey hain to jawab diya ke surkh honey ko . phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhii bataao , Allah Taala ke hukm se phalon par koi aafat aa jaey, to tum apne bhai ka maal aakhir kis cheez ke badley logey?"
2199,"aik shakhs ne agar pukhta honey se pahley hi (darakht par) phal khareedey, phir un par koi aafat aa gaee to jitna nuqsan hua, wo sab asl Malik ko bharnaa padega. mujhey Saalim-bin-Abdullaah ne khabar di, aur unhein Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, pukhta honey se pahley phalon ko na becho, aur na darakht par lagi hui khajoor ko tootii hui khajoor ke badley mein becho."
2200,ham ne Ibrahim ke samney qarz mein girwii rakhney ka zikr kya to unhon-ne kaha ke usmein koi harj nahi hai. phir ham se Aswad ke waaste se bayan kya ke unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne muqarrara muddat ke qarz par aik Yahudi se ghalla khareedaa aur apni zirah uske yahan girwii rakhi thi.
2201,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar mein aik shakhs ko tehseel daar banaya. wo sahib aik umda qism ki khajoor laey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya khaibar ki tamam khajoor isi tarah ki hoti hain. unhon-ne jawab diya ke nahi Allah ki qasam, ya Rasulullah ! ham to isi tarah aik saa khajoor (is se ghatiyaa khajooron ke) 2 saa de kar khareedtey hain. aur 2 saa teen saa ke badley mein letey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aisa na karo. albatta ghatiyaa khajoor ko pahley bech kar un peson se achi qism ki khajoor khareed saktey ho."
2202,"rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar mein aik shakhs ko tehseel daar banaya. wo sahib aik umda qism ki khajoor laey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya khaibar ki tamam khajoor isi tarah ki hoti hain. unhon-ne jawab diya ke nahi Allah ki qasam, ya Rasulullah ! ham to isi tarah aik saa khajoor (is se ghatiyaa khajooron ke) 2 saa de kar khareedtey hain. aur 2 saa teen saa ke badley mein letey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aisa na karo. albatta ghatiyaa khajoor ko pahley bech kar un peson se achi qism ki khajoor khareed saktey ho."
2203,jo bhi khajoor ka darakht pewand lagaaney ke baad bechaa jaey aur bechtey waqt phalon ka koi zikr na hua ho to phal usi ke hongey jisne pewand lagaya hai. ghulam aur khait ka bhi yahi haal hai. Naafe ne un teenon chizon ka naam liya tha.
2204,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya agar kisi ne khajoor ke aisey darakht bechey hon jinko pewandii kya ja chuka tha to uska phal bechney waley hi ka rehta hai. albatta agar kharidney waley ne shart laga di ho. (ke phal samet saudaa ho raha hai to phal bhi khareedaar ki milkiyat mein aa jaaeinge) .
2205,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzaabna se mana farmaya, yani baagh ke phalon ko agar wo khajoor hain to tootii hui khajoor ke badley mein naap kar bechaa jaey. aur agar angoor hain to usey khushk angoor ke badley naap kar bechaa jaey aur agar wo kheti hai to naap kar ghalla ke badley mein bechaa jaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un tamam qismon ke lein-dein se mana farmaya hai."
2206,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jis shakhs ne bhi kisi khajoor ke darakht ko pewandii banaya. phir us darakht hi ko bech diya to (us mausam ka phal) usi ka hoga jisne pewandii kya hai, lekin agar khareedaar ne phalon ki bhi shart laga di hai (to ye alag baat hai)."
2207,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muhaaqla, mukhaazra, mulaamisa, munaabiza aur Muzaabna se mana farmaya hai."
2208,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne darakht ko) زهو‏ . Mina ( se pahley tootii hui khajoor ke badley bechney se mana farmaya, ham ne puchha ke) زهو‏ . Mina ( kya hai? unhon-ne farmaya ke wo paak ke surkh ho jaey ya zard ho jaey. tum hi bataao ke agar Allah ke hukm se phal na aa saka to tum kis cheez ke badley main apne bhai ( khareedaar (ka maal apne liye halal karogey."
2209,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khajoor ka gabha kha rahe they. usi waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke darakhton mein aik darakht mard momin ki misal hai mere dil mein aaya ke kahun ke ye khajoor ka darakht hai, lekin haaziriin mein, main hi sabse chhoti Umr ka tha (is liye bataur adab mein chup raha ( phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud hi farmaya ke wo khajoor ka darakht hai."
2210,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko abu-Taiba ne pachhna lagaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein aik saa khajoor ( mazdoorii mein) dene ka hukm farmaya aur uske maalikon se farmaya ke wo uske khiraaj mein kuchh kami kar dein.
2211,Abu-Sufiyan kanjoos aadmi hai. to kya agar main unke maal se chipa kar kuchh ley liya karun to koi harj hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum apne liye aur apne beton ke liye nek-niyatii ke sath itna ley sakti ho jo tum sab ke liye kafi ho jaya kare.
2212,(qur'aan ki aayat) (ومن كان غنيا فليستعفف ومن كان فقيرا فليأكل بالمعروف) jo shakhs maaldaar ho wo (apni zere-parwarish yateem ka maal Hazam karne se) apne ko bachaaey aur jo faqeer ho wo nek-niyatii ke sath usmein se kha ley. ''ye aayat yatimon ke un sar-paraston ke mutaalliq nazil hui thi jo unki aur unke maal ki nigrani aur dekh bhaal kartey hon ke agar wo faqeer hain to (is khidmat ke iwaz) nek-niyatii ke sath usmein se kha saktey hain.
2213,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Shufaa ka haq har us maal mein qarar diya tha jo taqseem na hua ho, lekin uski had-bandii ho jaey aur rastey bhi pher diye jayen to ab Shufaa ka haq baqi nahi raha."
2214,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne har aisey maal mein Shufaa ka haq qaaim rakha jo taqseem na hua ho, lekin jab uski hudood qaaim ho gaee hon aur rasta bhi pher diya gaya ho to ab Shufaa ka haq baqi nahi raha."
2215,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, teen shakhs kahin bahar ja rahe they ke achcha barish honey lagi unhon-ne aik pahaad ke ghaar mein ja kar panah li. ittifaq se pahaad ki aik chattaan uper se ludhakii (aur us ghaar ke munh ko band kar diya jis mein ye teenon panah liye huey they) ab aik ne doosrey se kaha ke apne sabse achchhey amal ka jo tum ne kabhi kya ho, naam lekar Allah Taala se dua karo. is par unmein se aik ne ye dua ki ''aey Allaah! mere maan-baap bahut hi boodhey they. main bahar ley ja kar apne maweshii charaataa tha. phir jab Sham ko wapas aata to unka doodh nikaaltaa aur bartan mein pahley apne waalidain ko pesh karta. jab mere waalidain pi chuktey to phir bachchon ko aur apni biwi ko pilaataa. ittifaq se aik raat waapsii mein der ho gaee aur jab main ghar lota to waalidain so chukey they. usne kaha ke phir maine pasand nahi kya ke unhein jagaaoon bachchey mere qadmon mein bhookey padey ro rahe they. main barabar doodh ka piyala liye waalidain ke samney isi tarah khada raha yahan tak ke subah ho gaee. aey Allaah! agar terey nazdeek bhi maine ye kaam sirf teri raza hasil karne ke liye kya tha, to hamarey liye us chattaan ko hata kar itna rasta to bana de ke ham aasman ko to dekh sakein'' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, chunanche wo patthar kuchh hat gaya. doosrey shakhs ne dua ki ''aey Allah ! to khub janta hai ke mujhey apne chacha ki aik ladki se itni zyada mohabbat thi jitni aik mard ko kisi aurat se ho sakti hai. us ladki ne kaha tum mujh se apni khahish us waqt tak poori nahi kar saktey jab tak mujhey so ashrafii na de do. maine unke hasil karne ki koshish ki, aur aakhir itni ashrafii jama kar li. phir jab main uski donon raanon ke darmyan baithaa. to wo bolii, Allah se dar, aur mehar ko naajaaiz tareeqey par na tod. is par main khada ho gaya aur maine usey chhod diya. ab agar terey nazdeek bhi maine ye amal teri hi raza ke liye kya tha to hamarey liye (nikalney ka ( rasta bana de'' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, chunanche wo patthar 2 tehai hat gaya. teesrey shakhs ne dua ki ''aey Allah ! to janta hai ke maine aik mazdoor se aik farq Juwaar par kaam karaya tha. jab maine uski mazdoorii usey de di to usne leney se inkar kar diya. maine us juwaar ko lekar bo diya (khetii jab katii to usmein itni juwaar paida hui) us se maine aik bail aur aik charwaha khareed liya. kuchh arsa baad phir us ne aa kar mazdoorii mangi ke Allah ke bandey mujhey mera haq de-dey. maine kaha ke us bail aur uske charwaahey ke paas jao ke ye tumhari hi milkiyat hain. usne kaha ke mujh se mazaaq kartey ho. maine kaha ''main mazaaq nahi kartaa'' waqei ye tumharey hi hain. to aey Allaah! agar terey nazdeek ye kaam maine sirf teri raza hasil karne ke liye kya tha to yahan hamarey liye (is chattaan ko hata kar) rasta bana de. chunanche wo ghaar pura khul gaya aur wo teenon shakhs bahar aa gaey."
2216,ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein maujood they ke aik mustandaa lambey qad wala mushrik bakriyan haanktaa hua aaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya ke ye bechney ke liye hain ya Atiya hain? ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ke (ye bechney ke liye hain) ya hiba karne ke liye? usne kaha ke nahi balke bechney ke liye hain. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se aik bakri khareed li.
2217,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Ibrahim ne Saara (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath (Namrood ke mulk se) hijrat ki to aik aisey Shahar mein pahunchey jahan aik badshah rehta tha ya (ye farmaya ke) aik zaalim badshah rehta tha. us se Ibrahim ke mutaalliq kisi ne keh diya ke wo aik bahut hi khoobsurat aurat lekar yahan aaey hain. badshah ne aap (Alaihissalam) se puchhwaa bheja ke Ibrahim (al)! ye aurat jo tumharey sath hai tumhari kya hoti hai? unhon-ne farmaya ke ye meri behan hai. phir jab Ibrahim Saara (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan aaey to unse kaha ke meri baat na jhutlaanaa, main tumhen apni behan keh aaya hun. Allah ki qasam! aaj poori zameen par mere aur tumharey siwa koi momin nahi hai. chunanche aap (Alaihissalam) ne Saara (Raziallahu anhu) ko badshah ke yahan bhejaa, ya badshah Saara (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya. us waqt Saara (Raziallahu anhu) wuzu karke Namaz padhney khadi ho gaee thin. unhon-ne Allah ke huzoor mein ye dua ki ke ''aey Allah ! agar main tujh par aur terey rasool (Ibraaheem (al)) par eman rakhti hun aur agar maine apne shauhar ke siwa apni sharmgah ki hifazat ki hai, to too mujh par aik kaafir ko musallat na kar.'' itney mein badshah tharraaya aur iska paon zameen mein dhans gaya. Aaraj ne kaha ke abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne bayan kya, unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, ke Saara (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allah ke huzoor mein dua ki ke aey Allaah! agar ye mar gaya to log kahengey ke usi ne maara hai. chunanche wo phir chhoot gaya aur Saara (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf badhaa. Saara (Raziallahu anhu) wuzu karke phir Namaz padhney lagi thin aur ye dua karti jati thin ''aey Allaah! agar main tujh par aur terey rasool par eman rakhti hun aur apne shauhar (Ibraaheem (al)) ke siwa aur har mauqe par maine apni sharmgah ki hifazat ki hai to to mujh par us kaafir ko musallat na kar.'' chunanche wo phir tharraaya, kaanpaa aur uske paon zameen mein dhans gaey. Abdur-Rehman ne bayan kya ke abu-Salma ne bayan kya Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se ke Saara (Raziallahu anhu) ne phir wahi dua ki ke ''aey Allaah! agar ye mar gaya to log kahengey ke isi ne maara hai.'' ab dusri martaba ya teesri martaba bhi wo badshah chhod diya gaya. aakhir wo kehney laga ke tum logon ne mere yahan aik shaitan bhej diya. usey Ibrahim ke paas ley jao aur unhein Hajra ko bhi de do. phir saara Ibrahim ke paas aaiin aur unse kaha ke dekhtey nahi Allah ne kaafir ko kis tarah zaleel kya aur sath mein aik ladki bhi dilwaa di."
2218,"Sad-bin-abi-Waqas aur abd-bin-Zam'a (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik bachchey ke barey mein jhagdaa hua. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! ye mere bhai Utba-bin-abii-waqaas ka betaa hai. us ne wasiiyat ki thi ke ye ab iska betaa hai. aap khud mere bhai se uski mushabihat (similarity) dekh lein. lekin abd-bin-Zam'a (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ya Rasulullah! ye to mera bhai hai. mere bap ke bistar par paida hua hai. aur uski baandi ke pet ka hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bachchey ki sura dekhi to saaf Utba se miltii thi. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi farmaya ke aey abd! ye bachcha terey hi sath rahega, kyonke bachcha faraash ke taabe hota hai aur zaanii ke hisse mein sirf patthar hai aur aey Sauda-binte-Zam'a! us ladkey se to parda kya kar, chunanche Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ne phir usey kabhi nahi dekha."
2219,Allah se dar aur apne bap ke siwa kisi aur ka betaa na ban. Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar mujhey itni itnii daulat bhi mil jaey to bhi main ye kehna pasand nahi karta. magar waqia ye hai ke main to bachpan hi mein churaa liya gaya tha.
2220,"unhon-ne puchha ya Rasulullah! un nek kaamon ke mutaalliq aap ka kya hukm hai, jinhein main jahiliyat ke zamane mein sila rehmii, ghulam aazad karne aur sadqa dene ke silsile mein kya karta tha kya un aamaal ka bhi mujhey sawab milega? Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jitni nekiyan tum pahley kar chukey ho un sab ke sath Islam laey ho."
2221,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka guzar aik murda bakri par hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke iske chamdey se tum logon ne kyon nahi fayda uthaayaa? sahaba ne arz kya, ke wo to murdar hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke murdar ka sirf khana mana hai."
2222,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, wo zamana aaney wala hai jab ibne-Maryam (Eisaa (al)) tum mein aik aadil aur munsif Hakim ki haisiyat se utrengey. wo saleeb ko tod daalengey, suwaron ko mar daalengey aur jiziya ko khatm kar dengey. us waqt maal ki itni zyadti hogi ke koi leney wala na rahega."
2223,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko malum hua ke falan shakhs ne sharab bechii hai, to aap ne farmaya ke usey Allah Taala tabah w barbad kar de. kya usey malum nahi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha, Allah Taala yahood ko barbad karey ke charbi un par haram ki gaee thi lekin un logon ne usey pighlaa kar bechaa."
2224,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Allah yahudiyon ko tabah karey, zaalimon par charbi haram kar di gaee thi, lekin unhon-ne usey bech kar uski qeemat khaaii."
2225,"main Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir tha ke aik shakhs unke paas aaya, aur kaha ke aey abu-Abbaas ! main un logon mein se hon, jinki rozii apne hath ki dastkaarii par moquf hai aur main ye moortein banata hun. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par farmaya ke main tumhen sirf wahi baat batlaaoonga jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hai. unhon-ne kaha ke maine aapko ye farmatey huey suna tha ke jisne bhi koi moorat banai to Allah Taala usey us waqt tak azab karta rahega jab tak wo shakhs apni moorat mein jaan na daal de aur wo kabhi usmein jaan nahi daal sakta (ye sun kar) us shakhs ka saans chadh gaya aur chehra zard pad gaya. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke afsos! agar tum moortein Bunani hi chahtey ho to un darakhton ki aur har us cheez ki jis mein jaan nahi hai moortein bana saktey ho. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba ne Nazar-bin-Anas se sirf yahi aik hadis suni hai."
2226,jab sura al-Baqara ki tamam aayatein nazil ho chukiin to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey aur farmaya ke sharab ki sodagari haram qarar di gaee hai.
2227,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Allah Taala ka irshad hai ke teen tarah ke log aisey hongey jinka qiyamat ke din main muddaii banoonga, aik wo shakhs jisne mere naam par ahad kya aur wo tod diya, wo shakhs jisne kisi aazad insan ko bech kar uski qeemat khaaii aur wo shakhs jisne koi mazdoor ujrat par rakhaa, us se poori tarah kaam liya, lekin uski mazdoorii nahi di."
2228,qaidiyon mein Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) bhi thin. pahley to wo Dahiya Kalbi (Raziallahu anhu) ko milein phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke nikah mein aaiin.
2229,"wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they. (eik Ansari sahabi ne) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke ya Rasulullah! ladai mein ham laundiyon ke paas hambistari ke liye jatey hain. hamara irada unhein bechney ka bhi hota hai. to aap azl kar leney ke mutaalliq kya farmatey hain? is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, achchha tum log aisa kartey ho? agar tum aisa na karo phir bhi koi harj nahi. isliye ke jis Rooh ki bhi paidaaish Allah Taala ne qismat mein likh di hai wo paida ho kar hi rahegi ."
2230,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mudabbir ghulam bechaa tha.
2231,mudabbir ghulam ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bechaa tha.
2232,"un donon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap se ghair shadi shuda baandi ke mutaalliq jo zina kar ley sawal kya gaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey kode lagaao, phir agar wo zina kar ley to usey kode lagaao aur phir usey bech do. (aakhirii jumla aap ne) teesri ya chothi martaba ke baad (farmaayaa tha) ."
2233,"un donon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap se ghair shadi shuda baandi ke mutaalliq jo zina kar ley sawal kya gaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey kode lagaao, phir agar wo zina kar ley to usey kode lagaao aur phir usey bech do. ( aakhiri jumla aap ne) teesri ya chothi martaba ke baad) farmaya tha) ."
2234,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maine khud suna hai ke jab koi baandi zina kiraaey aur wo Sabit ho jaey to is par hade-zinaa jari ki jaey, albatta usey laanat malaamat na ki jaey. phir agar wo zina kiraaey to is par us martaba bhi had jari ki jaey, lekin kisi qism ki laanat malaamat na ki jaey. teesri martaba bhi agar zina karey aur zina Sabit ho jaey to usey bech daley chahe baal ki aik rassii ke badley hi kyon na ho."
2235,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khaibar tashrif laey aur Allah Taala ne qil'a fateh kara diya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney Safiya-binte-Huyi bin akhtab (Raziallahu anhu) ke Husan ki tareef ki gaee. unka shauhar qatl ho gaya tha. wo khud abhi dulhan thin. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein apne liye pasand kar liya. phir rawaangii hui. jab aap Sadde-Rohaa pahunchey to padao hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahin unke sath khilwat ki. phir aik chhotey dastar-khuwaan par hees taiyaar karke rakhwaayaa aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba se farmaya ke apne qareeb ke logon ko waleeme ki khabar kar do. Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath nikah ka yahi walima Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha. phir jab ham Madina ki taraf chaley to maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ek chadar se Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye parda karaya aur apne oont ko paas bitha kar apna takhna bichhaa diya. Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) apna paon Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke takhney par rakh kar Sawar ho gaiin.
2236,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, fateh Makka ke saal Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aap ka qiyam abhi Makka hi mein tha ke Allah aur uske rasool ne sharab , murdar , Sura aur buton ka bechna haram qarar de diya hai. is par puchha gaya ke ya Rasulullah ! murdar ki charbi ke mutaalliq kya hukm hai? usey ham kashtiyon par maltey hain. khaalon par us se tel ka kaam letey hain aur log us se apne charagh bhi jalaatey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi wo haram hai. usi mauqe par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah yahudiyon ko barbad karey Allah Taala ne jab charbi un par haram ki to un logon ne pighlaa kar usey bechaa aur uski qeemat khaaii. abu-Aasim ne kaha ke ham se abdul-hameed ne bayan kya, unse Yazeed ne bayan kya, unhein Ata ne likha ke maine Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
2237,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuttey ki qeemat, zaaniya ki ujrat aur kaahin ki ujrat se mana farmaya tha."
2238,"maine apne walid ko dekha ke aik pachhna lagaaney waley ( ghulam ( ko khareed rahe hain. is par maine iske mutaalliq unse puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khoon ki qeemat, kuttey ki qeemat, baandi ki) naajaaiz ( kamaaii se mana farmaya tha aur godney waaliyon aur gudwaaney waaliyon, sood leney walon aur dene walon par laanat ki thi aur tasweer banaaney waley par bhi laanat ki thi."
